  </head>
  <body>
    <div id="app_wrap" class="ema613_06_ih_0007">
      <section class="title type2">
        <h2 data-head="7" class="is_star" lang="y">은호는 넓이가 24.2 ㎡인 벽을 칠하는데 페인트 4 L를 사용했습니다. 페인트 1 L로 벽을 몇 ㎡ 칠한셈인지 식을 쓰고 답을 구해 보세요.</h2>
      </section>

      <section class="contents">
        <div class="question_box justify_center">
          <div class="img_area">
            <img src="./../../common_practice/img/EMA613_06_IH/0007_01.png" alt="" />
          </div>
          <div class="input_area flex dir_col align_end">
            <div class="input_row">
              <span lang="y" class="label_gray">식</span>
              <div class="input_wrap input1">
                <math-field data-answer-single="24.2÷4"></math-field>
              </div>
              =
              <div class="input_wrap input2">
                <math-field data-answer-single="6.05"></math-field>
              </div>
            </div>
            <div class="input_row">
              <span lang="y" class="label_gray">답</span>
              <div class="input_wrap input2">
                <math-field data-answer-single="6.05"></math-field>
              </div>
              ㎡
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>

        <!-- 해설 -->
        <div class="solve_area">
          <div class="inner_solve">
            <div class="flex">
              <strong class="tit_solve" lang="y">해설</strong>
              <div class="conts_solve">
                <p lang="y">(페인트 1 L로 칠한 벽의 넓이)</br>
                  =24.2÷4=6.05 (m&sup2;)</p>
              </div>
            </div>
            <div class="buttons_solve"></div>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="btn_area">
          <button class="btnType key">입력타입토글</button>
          <button class="btnReset">리셋</button>
          <button class="btnCheck">확인</button>
        </div>
      </section>
    </div>
